description:
This is a 30 minute workout called 'Adv Elliptical Workout: HIIT Elliptical for Strong Legs and Core | Fitscope Studio' from the channel Fitscope.
The workout falls under Cardio/Elliptical and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Other for this workout.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: #EllipticalWorkout #HIIT #Coreworkout #HIITElliptical #HIITWorkout #lowerbodyworkout
Adv Elliptical Workout: HIIT Elliptical for Strong Legs and Core | Fitscope Studio

Join Julia for this complete lower body workout. The entire leg muscle group is toned and strengthen with a combination of backward/forward intervals, standing calf raises, speed intervals and more. Incline is set at a constant 2% throughout. Soundtrack is an eclectic mix of hip hop, rock and pop. (HIP HOP LYRICS ARE EXPLICIT).
